export default {
    btn: {
        backgroundColor: '#336699',
        border: '0px',
        height: '40px',
        color: '#fff',
        fontFamily: 'Arial',
        fontSize: '13px',
        fontWeight: 'bold',
        lineHeight: '40px',
        textTransform: 'uppercase',
        textShadow: '0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2)',
        background: 'url(../../../images/line_menu.PNG) no-repeat right center',
        cursor: 'pointer',
    },
    mainNavbar: {
        maxWidth: '980px',
        margin: '0 auto',
        height: '40px',
        padding: '0 10px',
        display: 'inline-block'
    }
}
